high_descs: Go forward and to the left to the black round table.
Take the large knife next to the plant from the table.
Turn left, go to the wall, turn right, go to the table.
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices.
Turn around, go forward, turn left after passing the table, go forward to the fridge.
Put the knife on the shelf with the cup in the fridge.
Turn around, go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward to the wall, turn right, go to the table.
Take a slice of lettuce from the table.
Turn around, go to the door, turn left go forward, turn left after passing the table, go forward to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce on the lowest left shelf of the fridge.
Turn left, go towards the wall, turn left, go to the black round table.
Put the lettuce below the plant on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Move to stand in front of the round kitchen table.
Pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle from the table.
Move closer to the edge of the table closest to the wall while carrying the knife.
Use the knife to slice the head of lettuce on the table.
Move to the fridge while carrying the knife.
Open the fridge and place the knife on the top shelf.
Move back to the far side of the table so you're close to the head of lettuce again.
Pick up the end slice of lettuce from the table.
Carry the slice of lettuce to the fridge.
Place the lettuce on the top shelf of the fridge and then remove after a few seconds.
Carry the lettuce to the edge of the table closest to the fridge, so you're standing directly to the right of the chair.
Place the lettuce on the table between the pepper grinder and plant.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled piece of lettuce on the kitchen table.

high_descs: Go towards the round table.
Take the large knife from the table.
Move over to the left while facing the table.
Cut the lettuce into slices.
Turn right, go straight, when past the table turn left, go straight to the fridge.
Put the knife on the bottom shelf of the fridge.
Turn around, go straight, when past the table turn right, go straight to the wall, turn right to face the table.
Take a slice of lettuce.
Turn right, go straight, when past the table turn left, go straight to the fridge.
Put the lettuce on the bottom shelf of the fridge. Close then open the fridge. Take the lettuce from the fridge.
Turn left, go towards the wall, turn left to face the round table.
Put the lettuce on the table to the bottom left of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Walk up to the black, round table.
Pick up the knife, laying on the table, in front of the plant.
Move to the left, between the wall and the head of lettuce on the table.
Cut the lettuce into slices.
Turn right and walk around the table, then across the room, to the refrigerator.
Place the knife in the refrigerator, on the shelf above the drawers.
Turn around and walk back to the table where the lettuce is.
Pick up one of the slices of lettuce.
Turn right, walk around the table, and across the room, back to the refrigerator.
Place the lettuce in the refrigerator, beside the knife, shut the refrigerator door, wait a moment, and take the lettuce back out of the refrigerator.
Turn around facing the front door and the table.
Place the lettuce on the table, between the plant and the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold slice of lettuce on the dining table.

high_descs: Move forward to the black table.
Pick up the knife from the table
Move to the left to stand in front of the lettuce.
Slice the lettuce up with the knife.
Go to the fridge behind the black table.
Open the fridge and put the knife inside, then close the fridge.
Turn around and go back to the lettuce on the table.
Pick up one slice of the lettuce.
Go back to the fridge with the lettuce.
Open the fridge and put the lettuce inside, next to the knife.
Take the lettuce out of the fridge.
Take the lettuce back to the black table and set it in the center of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of lettuce in the center of a table.
